mpd-tools
=========

`mpd-tools` is a collection of scripts to control [mpd][].

* mpd-goodsong.sh copyright pbrisbin

## Dependencies

### Global
* coreutils

### mpd-artist && mpd-song
* netcfg

## Exit codes
    0   - successful
    1   - bad argument
    2   - file not found

